🔵 Part 2: Introduction to SQL
1️⃣ What is SQL? – Uses in IT, Pharma, Decision Making
2️⃣ SQL Data Types (8 Common Types)
3️⃣ Create a Table – CREATE TABLE, PRAGMA Table_Info(tableName)
4️⃣ Insert Data – INSERT INTO (SQLite allows any type, others don’t)
5️⃣ Select Data – SELECT
🔹 All rows & columns
🔹 Specific rows & columns (WHERE clause)
6️⃣ Update Data – UPDATE (Modify using SET, WHERE)
7️⃣ Delete Data – DELETE
🔹 Remove all rows
🔹 Remove specific rows (WHERE)
8️⃣ Drop a Table – DROP TABLE (Permanently delete)
9️⃣ Modify a Table – ALTER TABLE
🔹 Add, rename, or remove columns
